Ramsay Ames https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramsay_Ames 0 Ramsay Ames (born Phillips Ames, March 30, 1919 – March 30, 1998) was a leading 1940s American B movie actress, model, dancer, pin-up girl and television host. She appeared in the film The Mummy's Ghost (1944), where she played the Princess Ananka.
